Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, d nutni i ten-ițṛaǧun ; lameɛna aṭas n yiqeddacen i llan di leqdic ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi, a sen-yefk tazmert s wayes ara nefṛeq i yiman-nsen.
Ma d kečč m'ara tseddqeḍ, ilaq afus-ik ayeffus ur ițwali ara wayen ixeddem ansi i d-yekka ;
Exdem lmeǧhud-ik iwakken a ț-yɣumm s tigzirt, s tigellilt yellan deg umkan-agi, ama di teftilt m'ara yeskkuɛ uyaziḍ.
