Ma yella bɣiɣ aț-țfehmem acḥal hraw, acḥal ɣezzif, acḥal lqay, acḥal ɛlay leḥmala n Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țenɛețțabem iwakken aț-țeččeḍ.
Ula d kečč aț-țeččem kra n lemqamat, tzemrem a t-tɛeṣṣab seg weɣṛum-nni n wass amezwaru.
Ma yella kečč i d-ițwagezmen seg uḥeccad, tețțuleqmeḍ ɣef tzemmurt n lɛali ɣas akken d aḥeccad i telliḍ, acḥal ihi i sen-ishel i nutni yellan ț-țiṣeḍwa n tzemmurt iwakken ad uɣalen ad țțuleqmen ɣef tzemmurt-nsen.
