Lejdud-nni n tmes i d-yețbanen s ufella, am akken d amextaf ( tamsal. )
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tejreḥ tasa-agi, ț-ținezmarin n tmes i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda ɣer tmurt n Yahuda yellan ț-țigzirt n Lus.
Di leǧwahi-nni, llan azal n meyya uɛecrin n wayetmaten, țemyezwaǧen wway gar-asen iwakken ad ilin azal n tlata alaf n yergazen.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, a ț-issers ɣef yixef n igenwan iwakken kra n yemdanen ad ifennu, s wakka ad kecmen deg imukan imezwura, mkul yiwen seg-sen i deg yella.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Russu.
