Axaṭer llant azal n meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa ara nemmeslay i yemdanen, lameɛna wiyaḍ xedmen akken i t-id-iweṣṣa iwakken ad nɣen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed.
A d-nefk lemtel n dduzan n lmusiqa am tjewwaqt d snitra : ma yella ur yemxalaf ara ttejṛa, ur nețțuɣal ara a d-yedṛu yid-es.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d win iwumi ur iɣelli ara di tserwiḥin nniḍen, nețțat daɣen i d-țeffɣen seg-s.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lmut.
Ațan ihi tcaquṛt thegga ɣer izuṛan n ttjuṛ, yal yiwen deg waklan s zzit.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) yerna a d-zzin fell-as.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țsetḥin ara s uḥellel-nsen iwakken a d-rreɣ ɣer idurar n lebḥeṛ, ad rren lxiṛ s waṭas n leḥyuḍ n ddheb, iwakken a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, ad awekklen ayen akk i t-ițṛaǧun.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen yelhan,
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen wemkan i deg llan lbabuṛ akk-d wid ur neḍhiṛ ṛṛuǧen, yusa-d ɣer uweḥḥi-nni isem-is, win akken i t-id-yusan si tmurt n Masidunya, ama s leḥjab yellan di mkul amkan ;
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a k-id-yaf di tegzirt n Kritus si zik.
